{"tid":2430334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共人大代表提案「藝人一次吸毒終身禁演」","createTime":"2021-03-03T01:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T12:35:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":95,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ae2de1abe39aa135b970b22e4fc0077ce246e1ca","tid":2430334,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:02:08.000Z","msg":"鑑於中國藝人不時傳出吸毒，至今未絕，有中國全國人大代表準備提案，建議以法律明文規定「一次吸毒，終身禁演」，防止涉毒藝人鑽漏洞變相復出，甚至以「改過自新」作為炒作題材。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，提出這項建議案的是廣東籍全國人大代表、兼任律師事務所主任的朱列玉。他指出，近年明星吸毒的醜聞頻繁曝光，而中國娛樂圈涉毒亂象的背後，顯現的是行業規範、社會輿論對明星禁毒的不足，以及法律、法規的缺漏。<br />\n<br />\n朱列玉表示，截至2019年底，中國吸毒者有214.8萬人。其中，濫用大麻者以外籍人士、有境外學習或工作經歷者及演藝人員為主。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，儘管中國行業規範及地方性法規對明星涉毒行為有一定程度懲戒，但目前的措施仍不足以遏止這種亂象，部分涉毒藝人仍能鑽制度漏洞亮相。若不嚴令禁止他們再次踏足演藝圈，會讓其他藝人看到即使吸毒也可以復出，甚至可以打著「改過自新」的旗號炒作。<br />\n<br />\n朱列玉說，如果這類藝人不被禁演，反會因為醜聞炒作獲得更多的關注和利益。因此，法律應準確界定「禁演」範圍，明確利益相關人員及公司的連帶責任。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，限制涉毒藝人的影視作品播放是特殊職業的屬性問題，就像有傳染病的人就不能當廚師，有性侵、性騷擾史的人就不能當老師一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://news.tvbs. com.tw/life/1471140</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT17dqp5howBM_wC-0hdZzAL9ubrIGIWI1VRQ&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcT17dqp5howBM_wC-0hdZzAL9ubrIGIWI1VRQ%26usqp%3DCAU&h=7bbf7c46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55e57f4e83a30fb6b7460aedd69c54340f802140","tid":2430334,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:03:32.000Z","msg":"其實要"},{"pid":"77f0257a606270bd5f9ea3b7af823ce7486160d0","tid":2430334,"uid":230530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:04:04.000Z","msg":"楊明？"},{"pid":"79c8aef32a185f488688241a2061406e69ccc4f5","tid":2430334,"uid":41343,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:04:24.000Z","msg":"所以中国拍唔出Iron Man"},{"pid":"ea1da6762a50f9d659fed2e64a1adf2f673a4241","tid":2430334,"uid":298796,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"醉駕重影響安全啦, 我覺得都要<br />\n等條羊鳴咁撚申77"},{"pid":"b707497afbb6bae2438077509b39dbef1a5fdd93","tid":2430334,"uid":352697,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:06:07.000Z","msg":"除非你老豆係成蟲"},{"pid":"c30a064f9f1987d6c20720bfd287d9ea26c6d86a","tid":2430334,"uid":208376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"犯過刑事就終身禁演啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05e58d603e9759c58f740437d17e42731cc3e2e","tid":2430334,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"日本都係咁啦 衰吸毒唔洗撈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41cc740736093ab9cdedbed93f7552afb12d912","tid":2430334,"uid":23973,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:49:33.000Z","msg":"鬼國真係好撚戇鳩，將一啲social norms都要make 成laws。"},{"pid":"e973f2bd9b34c39d5430f5433688fddd6379985d","tid":2430334,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:51:25.000Z","msg":"楊明？"},{"pid":"05711d78222f3f66440301b588142d85c7e7fde2","tid":2430334,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"1. 蘇X康"},{"pid":"179acb51fc60adb08ae1fb09f81c8ea45619a5d3","tid":2430334,"uid":37413,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a05e58d603e9759c58f740437d17e42731cc3e2e","tid":2430334,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"日本都係咁啦 衰吸毒唔洗撈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:58:18.000Z","msg":"但人哋冇明文規定嘛"},{"pid":"9db323559b62d95e6ea498f399fccd745272952a","tid":2430334,"uid":183090,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"a05e58d603e9759c58f740437d17e42731cc3e2e","tid":2430334,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"r